<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPal3">
<l>cuṭaroḷi parantaṉa cūḻticai yellān tuṉṉiya tārakai miṉṉoḷi curuṅkip</l>
<l>paṭaroḷi pacuttaṉaṉ paṉimati yivaṉō pāyiru ḷakaṉṟatu paimpoḻil kamukiṉ</l>
<l>maṭaliṭaik kīṟivaṇ pāḷaika ṇāṟa vaikaṟai kūrntatu māruta mituvō</l>
<l>vaṭaloḷi tikaḻtaru tikiriyan taṭakkai yaraṅkattam māpaḷḷi yeḻuntaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The rays of the sun have spread around in all the directions.</l>
<l>The glittering lights of the crowding stars having dwindled,</l>
<l>is this one the cool Moon, with light that spreads, who has faded?</l>
<l>The pervasive darkness has vanished.</l>
<l>Is this the wind that [is blowing] abundantly at daybreak</l>
<l>slitting the middle of the areca-palms fronds in the green groves</l>
<l>so that the abundant spathes of palm emit a sweet smell?</l>
<l>O Lord of Raṅgam with large, beautiful hands [that bear] a deadly, brightly shining discus!</l>
<l>Do grace to wake up from sleep!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
